title: Let’s Talk Trades + TNF Preview, Party Time - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/10
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode as we enter Week 10! On today’s fantasy football podcast, let’s talk trades! Andy, Mike, and Jason discuss the most asked about players and specific trade scenarios! Plus, the Week 10 edition of Buy or Sell, and a preview of Thursday Night Football. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 10th, 2021.
  
 (04:40) - Buy or Sell
 (11:00) - News & Notes
 (27:50) - Let’s Talk Trades
 (29:00) - Antonio Gibson
 (34:40) - Aaron Jones
 (42:25) - Pat Freiermuth / T.J. Hockenson
 (50:00) - Darrell Henderson
 (56:45) - Thursday Night Breakdown - Ravens at Dolphins
